<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>OfficeBites</title>
    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com">
    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin>
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Space+Grotesk:wght@500;700&family=JetBrains+Mono:wght@400;500&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">

    <style>
        :root {
            --bg: #222222;
            --bg-card: #2b2b2b;
            --accent: #89e900;
            --accent-dim: #5c9c0d;
            --text: #F2F2F0;
            --text-dim: #8f8f8c;
            --line: #3a3a3a;
        }

        * { margin: 0; padding: 0; box-sizing: border-box; }

        body {
            background: var(--bg);
            color: var(--text);
            font-family: "Space Grotesk", sans-serif;
            min-height: 100vh;
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            padding: 48px 24px;
            position: relative;
            overflow-x: hidden;
        }

        /* faint grid texture, like ledger paper */
        body::before {
            content: "";
            position: absolute;
            inset: 0;
            background-image: linear-gradient(rgba(255,255,255,.025) 1px, transparent 1px);
            background-size: 100% 32px;
            pointer-events: none;
        }

        .eyebrow {
            font-family: "JetBrains Mono", monospace;
            font-size: 12px;
            letter-spacing: 3px;
            text-transform: uppercase;
            color: var(--accent);
            margin-bottom: 18px;
        }

        h1 {
            font-size: clamp(36px, 6vw, 64px);
            font-weight: 700;
            letter-spacing: -1.5px;
            line-height: 1.02;
            text-align: center;
            max-width: 780px;
        }

        h1 span {
            color: var(--accent);
        }

        .subtitle {
            margin-top: 18px;
            max-width: 480px;
            text-align: center;
            color: var(--text-dim);
            font-size: 15px;
            line-height: 1.6;
        }

        /* ── Token / Coupon Row ───────────────────── */
        .tokens {
            display: flex;
            flex-wrap: wrap;
            justify-content: center;
            gap: 24px;
            margin-top: 56px;
            z-index: 1;
        }

        .token {
            position: relative;
            width: 220px;
            background: var(--bg-card);
            border: 1px dashed var(--line);
            border-radius: 4px;
            padding: 26px 22px 22px;
            text-decoration: none;
            color: var(--text);
            transition: transform .25s ease, border-color .25s ease;
        }

        .token:hover {
            transform: translateY(-6px);
            border-color: var(--accent);
        }

        /* punch-hole notches, like a real ticket stub */
        .token::before,
        .token::after {
            content: "";
            position: absolute;
            width: 16px;
            height: 16px;
            background: var(--bg);
            border: 1px dashed var(--line);
            border-radius: 50%;
            top: 50%;
            transform: translateY(-50%);
        }
        .token::before { left: -9px; }
        .token::after { right: -9px; }

        .token-code {
            font-family: "JetBrains Mono", monospace;
            font-size: 11px;
            color: var(--accent-dim);
            letter-spacing: 1px;
        }

        .token-role {
            font-size: 20px;
            font-weight: 700;
            margin-top: 10px;
            margin-bottom: 6px;
        }

        .token-desc {
            font-size: 13px;
            color: var(--text-dim);
            line-height: 1.5;
        }

        .token-arrow {
            display: inline-block;
            margin-top: 16px;
            font-family: "JetBrains Mono", monospace;
            font-size: 12px;
            color: var(--accent);
        }

        /* ── Bottom actions ──────────────────────── */
        .actions {
            margin-top: 48px;
            display: flex;
            gap: 16px;
            align-items: center;
            z-index: 1;
        }

        .btn-primary {
            background: var(--accent);
            color: var(--bg);
            font-weight: 700;
            font-size: 14px;
            padding: 13px 28px;
            border-radius: 4px;
            text-decoration: none;
            transition: background .2s ease;
        }

        .btn-primary:hover {
            background: #a0ff00;
        }

        .btn-ghost {
            color: var(--text-dim);
            font-size: 14px;
            text-decoration: none;
            border-bottom: 1px solid var(--line);
            padding-bottom: 2px;
            transition: color .2s ease, border-color .2s ease;
        }

        .btn-ghost:hover {
            color: var(--text);
            border-color: var(--text-dim);
        }

        footer {
            margin-top: 64px;
            font-family: "JetBrains Mono", monospace;
            font-size: 11px;
            color: var(--text-dim);
            letter-spacing: 1px;
            z-index: 1;
        }

        @media (max-width: 500px) {
            .token { width: 100%; max-width: 280px; }
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>

    <div class="eyebrow">/ canteen management, sorted /</div>

    <h1>Every office lunch, <span>logged and settled.</span></h1>
    <p class="subtitle">
        OfficeBites keeps the canteen owner, the office, and the delivery run
        on the same page — one menu, one ledger, no missed bills.
    </p>

    <div class="tokens">
        <a href="/api/auth/login" class="token">
            <div class="token-code">NO. 01 — OWNER</div>
            <div class="token-role">Canteen</div>
            <div class="token-desc">Manage the menu, offices, agents & bills.</div>
            <div class="token-arrow">enter →</div>
        </a>

        <a href="/api/auth/login" class="token">
            <div class="token-code">NO. 02 — CLIENT</div>
            <div class="token-role">Office</div>
            <div class="token-desc">Check what came in, and what's owed.</div>
            <div class="token-arrow">enter →</div>
        </a>

        <a href="/api/auth/login" class="token">
            <div class="token-code">NO. 03 — AGENT</div>
            <div class="token-role">Delivery</div>
            <div class="token-desc">Log every drop-off, office by office.</div>
            <div class="token-arrow">enter →</div>
        </a>
    </div>

    <div class="actions">
        <a href="/api/auth/register" class="btn-primary">Register as Owner</a>
        <a href="/api/auth/login" class="btn-ghost">Already have an account? Sign in</a>
    </div>

    <footer>OFFICEBITES — EST. 2026</footer>

</body>
</html>